metadata.name: WILD ONES
metadata.description:
'...Halston hedonism'

A 1/1 original artwork by me, Kate Philipson.

A hedonistic party that would make the wildest night at Studio 54 looks tame. 

Beautiful women, sequins and glitter, 24-carat gold, and of course, the leopard. A recipe for debauchery. These are the WILD ONES. 

Of all the artworks I have created, this is my ultimate hero piece.  


5000 x 5977 px
JPEG
